MoreInformation.NoteLiteral:
**Entry requirements:**

- at least 90 ECTS completed at the undergraduate level;
- B2 level of English language proficiency.

**Documents to be submitted in English:**

- motivation letter - personal motivation to join the challenge, attitude towards experimenting and trying out new educational models, previous experience on the challenge topic;
- transcript of records - proof of enrolment in a Bachelor's or Master’s degree programme in one of the 13 ECIU university members, stating that completed at least 90 ECTS at the undergraduate level, and the study field/programme; not mandatory for KTU students;
- copy of ID card/passport in "other" - a document issued by the country of origin (needed for registration to university services); not mandatory for KTU students.

Please note that documents submitted not in English will not be processed further in the admission process.
